## 🔐 ETHICAL USAGE & RESTRICTIONS

This Software is provided for **ethical cybersecurity research, education, and authorized red team use** only.

You may NOT use the Software for any of the following purposes:

- 🚫 Unethical, harmful, or unlawful activity (e.g., unauthorized access, surveillance, exploitation)
- 🚫 Offensive cybersecurity actions without written client or asset owner consent
- 🚫 Deployment or training of AI for malicious purposes (e.g., phishing bots, automated malware delivery)
- 🚫 Use in political, military, or government surveillance operations without prior written permission
- 🚫 Commercial redistribution, monetization, or repackaging without explicit approval

Modules flagged as **"PRIVATE"**, **"RESTRICTED"**, or **"ENTERPRISE ONLY"** are subject to additional controls:

- 🔐 These modules may only be executed with valid authentication credentials
- 🛑 Unauthorized execution will result in limited functionality or complete disablement
- 📡 Some modules may communicate with a licensing or validation server to enforce access control

