## 🤖 AI MODULES CLAUSE

- AI-powered tools embedded in this Software may **not be used** to train, deploy, or operate malicious autonomous systems or decision-making models.
- AI suggestions, payload generators, and automation must be used strictly within **ethical pentesting scopes**, **lab simulations**, or **blue team training**.
- AI modules that connect to external APIs (e.g., LLMs) should not be used to impersonate individuals, generate targeted threats, or bypass security mechanisms.

